node.text: Love you tooooo. You know me best 🥰

#happybirthday #Hubby @zhongpinglim

Sadly this year we can’t go anywhere for celebration but you can finally have your peace of sleeping at wee hours and waking up only when you want to then game whole day.

#thankyou for remembering, although you’re #bday boy but you’re still my #Husband #thanks for loving me, #iloveyou and I promise to let you game till 0000 tonight.

#sginsta #sginstagram #sgcouple #sgplaces #throwback #circuitbreaker #stayhomesg
Love you tooooo. You know me best 🥰
